      <h1>Layered Anchored VWAP as a Framework for Regime Identification</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Inventory Persistence, Structural Migration, and Hierarchical Decay Across Five Flow Extremes</p>
      <div class="meta">Version: Feb 18 (snapshot). Figures embedded below. Click any figure to open a zoomable viewer (wheel to zoom, drag to pan, buttons for zoom/reset/fullscreen).</div>
    </div>

    <div class="paper">
